Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.39,0:00:19.48,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\be1\fax.15}冲破幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.48,0:00:21.90,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\be1\fax.15}用你的刚拳铁脚勇往直前
