Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.88,0:01:07.44,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\be1\fax.15}让你觉得碍眼的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.44,0:01:09.57,OP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\be1\fax.15}那还犹豫什么
